  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  stage IV melanoma (AJCC classification)

          -  minimum of 2 sc metastases

          -  failure or refusal of standard chemotherapy

          -  ECOG score of 0 or 1

          -  other

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  metastatic CNS disease

          -  ocular or mucosal melanoma

          -  immunodeficiency

          -  splenectomy

          -  other
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
